"title": "5398: loss",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5398",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>In a fallen world, believers are always liable to lose those things that they hold precious. Whilst offering comfort, Scripture urges believers to set their hearts upon eternal treasures, which cannot be lost.</p>\n<h2>Loss is part of a fallen world</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19\">MAT 6:19</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Loss of property</h2>\n<h3>Through theft</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:15\">JOB 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:17\">JOB 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>Through accident</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:39\">GEN 31:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:33-Exod21:34\">EXO 21:33–21:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:15\">EXO 22:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:5\">2KI 6:5</a></p>\n<h3>Through disaster</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:16\">JOB 1:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:10\">ACT 27:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:18-Acts27:21\">ACT 27:18–27:21</a></p>\n<h3>Through one's own fault</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:10-Prov6:11\">PRO 6:10–6:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:33-Prov24:34\">PRO 24:33–24:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:11\">PRO 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:18\">PRO 13:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:13\">LUK 15:13</a></p>\n<h3>Through the judgment of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:4\">JER 17:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:4\">MAL 1:4</a></p>\n<h2>Loss of family and friends</h2>\n<h3>Through bereavement</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:2\">GEN 23:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:34\">GEN 37:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:3\">GEN 50:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:29\">NUM 20:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:8\">DEU 34:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:21\">RUT 1:21</a> <em>Naomi had lost her husband and her two sons</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:18-2Sam12:23\">2SA 12:18–12:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:18-2Kgs4:21\">2KI 4:18–4:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:15-Ezek24:18\">EZK 24:15–24:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:11-Luke7:13\">LUK 7:11–7:13</a></p>\n<h3>Through violence and disaster</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:12\">2SA 1:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:18-Job1:19\">JOB 1:18–1:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:8-Isa47:9\">ISA 47:8–47:9</a></p>\n<h3>Through alienation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:13-Job19:22\">JOB 19:13–19:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:11-Ps31:12\">PSA 31:11–31:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:10-1Cor7:15\">1CO 7:10–7:15</a></p>\n<h2>Losses in warfare</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:11-Gen14:12\">GEN 14:11–14:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:17\">1SA 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:5\">1SA 23:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:1-1Sam30:2\">1SA 30:1–30:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:21\">1KI 20:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr13:17\">2CH 13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:17-2Chr36:20\">2CH 36:17–36:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:24\">LUK 21:24</a></p>\n<h2>Other kinds of loss</h2>\n<h3>Health and strength</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:9-Ps31:10\">PSA 31:9–31:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:3-Ps32:4\">PSA 32:3–32:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:3-Ps102:5\">PSA 102:3–102:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:11\">PSA 102:11</a></p>\n<h3>Reputation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:8\">PSA 102:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:8\">2CO 6:8</a></p>\n<h3>Dignity</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:15\">JOB 30:15</a></p>\n<h3>Power</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:31\">DAN 4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:26\">DAN 7:26</a></p>\n<h3>Employment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:1-Luke16:3\">LUK 16:1–16:3</a></p>\n<h3>Time</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:19\">EXO 21:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:9\">ACT 27:9</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual loss</h2>\n<h3>Of the ungodly</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:12-Prov6:15\">PRO 6:12–6:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:8-2Thess1:10\">2TH 1:8–1:10</a></p>\n<h3>Of the worldly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:26\">MAT 16:26</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:36\">MRK 8:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:25\">LUK 9:25</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:20-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:20–12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:16-Heb12:17\">HEB 12:16–12:17</a></p>\n<h3>Of the disobedient</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:26-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:26–7:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:49\">LUK 6:49</a></p>\n<h3>Of the Jewish nation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:6\">JER 50:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:43\">MAT 21:43</a></p>\n<h3>Of the lazy servant</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:26-Matt25:30\">MAT 25:26–25:30</a></p>\n<h3>Of the careless worker</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:12-1Cor3:15\">1CO 3:12–3:15</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Of the apostate</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4-Heb6:6\">HEB 6:4–6:6</a></p>\n<h2>Voluntary loss</h2>\n<h3>By Jesus Christ for the salvation of humanity</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:6-Phil2:11\">PHP 2:6–2:11</a></p>\n<h3>For Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:25\">MAT 16:25</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:35\">MRK 8:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:24\">LUK 9:24</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:7-Phil3:9\">PHP 3:7–3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:39\">MAT 10:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:12\">MAT 19:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:9-1Cor4:13\">1CO 4:9–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:34\">HEB 10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:24-Heb11:26\">HEB 11:24–11:26</a></p>\n<h2>Losses made good</h2>\n<h3>By restitution</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:19\">EXO 21:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:34\">EXO 21:34</a></p>\n<h3>By recovery</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:4\">LUK 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:8\">LUK 15:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:20\">LUK 15:20</a></p>\n<h3>By God's goodness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:10\">JOB 42:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:29-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:29–18:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:12\">ROM 11:12</a></p>\n<h2>God seeks the lost soul</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:10\">LUK 19:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:4\">LUK 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:8\">LUK 15:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:20\">LUK 15:20</a></p>\n<h2>Comfort in loss</h2>\n<h3>God's comfort</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:9\">PSA 146:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3-2Cor1:4\">2CO 1:3–1:4</a></p>\n<h3>The comfort of others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:11\">JOB 2:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:19\">JHN 11:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:28-Acts11:29\">ACT 11:28–11:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></p>\n<h2>Treasures that cannot be lost</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:20\">MAT 6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33\">LUK 12:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:22\">JHN 16:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a></p>",
